reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 102/11: DEEMING ORDER (NORTH ALMAGUIN PLANNING BOARD)
reg_info.act_under: Planning Act   Loi sur l'aménagement du territoire

content.content: 1. (1) Ontario Regulation 484/71, as it read immediately before this Regulation comes into force, shall be deemed to be and to always have been a by-law passed under section 34 of the Act by the North Almaguin Planning Board. O. Reg. 102/11, s. 1 (1). (2) The deemed by-law shall be referred to as by-law number 2011-01 of the North Almaguin Planning Board. O. Reg. 102/11, s. 1 (2).
content.raw_html:
